OL,3,CUK looks to Denmark to shake up
OL,4,Cimmigration system
OL,6,FHome Secretary Shabana Mahmood is set
OL,7,Fto announce a shakeup of Britain's
OL,8,Fimmigration rules with reforms
OL,9,Fmodelled on the Danish system, ITV
OL,10,FNews understands.
OL,12,FMahmood dispatched officials to the
OL,13,Fcountry last month to study its border
OL,14,Fcontrol and asylum policies, which are
OL,15,Fseen as some of the toughest in Europe.
OL,17,FDenmark's tighter rules on family
OL,18,Freunions and restricting some refugees
OL,19,Fto a temporary stay are among the
OL,20,Fpolicies being looked at.
