OL,3,CUK looks to Denmark to shake up
OL,4,Cimmigration system
OL,6,FIt comes after a difficult few months
OL,7,Ffor the government, which saw rising
OL,8,Fnumbers of small boat crossings in the
OL,9,FChannel and a migrant, who was
OL,10,Fdeported under the UK's returns deal
OL,11,Fwith France, re-enter the country.
OL,13,FMahmood wants deterrents in place to
OL,14,Fstop people seeking to enter Britain
OL,15,Fvia unauthorised routes, while making
OL,16,Fit easier to remove those who are
OL,17,Ffound to have no right to stay in the
OL,18,FUK.
