OL,3,CUK looks to Denmark to shake up
OL,4,Cimmigration system
OL,6,FSome 648 people crossed the Channel to
OL,7,FBritain in nine boats on Friday,
OL,8,Faccording to Home Office figures
OL,9,Fpublished on Saturday, bringing the
OL,10,Ftotal for the year so far to 38,223.
OL,12,FLabour MPs are split on the move. Some
OL,13,Fin so-called red wall seats, which are
OL,14,Fseen as vulnerable to challenge from
OL,15,FReform UK, want ministers to go
OL,16,Ffurther towards the Danish system.
