OL,3,CUK looks to Denmark to shake up
OL,4,Cimmigration system
OL,6,FNottingham East MP Nadia Whittome, who
OL,7,Fis a member of the party's Socialist
OL,8,FCampaign Group caucus, urged against
OL,9,Femulating the Danish model, suggesting
OL,10,Fit was "far-right".
OL,12,F"I think these are policies of the far-
OL,13,Fright. I don't think anyone wants to
OL,14,Fsee a Labour government flirting with
OL,15,Fthem," she said.
