OL,3,CUK looks to Denmark to shake up
OL,4,Cimmigration system
OL,6,FThe shakeup comes after Mahmood
OL,7,Fconceded on Thursday that the Home
OL,8,FOffice is "not yet fit for purpose"
OL,9,Fand has been "set up for failure",
OL,10,Ffollowing the release of a "damning"
OL,11,Freport into the government department.
OL,13,FThe review was carried out while the
OL,14,FConservative government was in power,
OL,15,Fand had been kept secret for more than
OL,16,Ftwo years before it was obtained by
OL,17,FThe Times following a legal challenge.
